title: Alessandro Sinno
text:
Alessandro Sinno (born 17 July 1994) is an Italian male <a href="pole%20vault">pole vault</a>er.
Biography.
He has won three times his <a href="Italian%20Athletics%20Championships">country's senior national championship</a>, and with his new <a href="Personal%20record">personal best</a>, ranked in the top 60, at 47th place, on the <a href="International%20Association%20of%20Athletics%20Federations">IAAF</a> world leading list at the 11 July 2018.
